story
-----
You are a dark wizard, once powerful but cast out of your realm by
the slightly darker wizard <insert name here>

Your aim is to retake the throne of darkest of dark lords.

Fight hoards of enemies, but keep them at a distance, as you are
physically weak. Use spells, missiles and summon allies each level
to assist you.

